content:
So, if I were going to make a tech manifesto, it might be something like:

- protocols not platforms
- coops and unions
- technology should not actively hurt us
- people not users
- seven generations, seven continents
- free markets require antitrust enforcement

content:
been a week already?....

I'm still for work, preferably full-time permanent position. Would absolutely love to do some #ESP32 related work, #ESPIDF/#FreeRTOS firmware development and/or #KiCAD #PCB work would be amazing.

#Python/#Django/#Flask would all be awesome too, I've really grown as a Django dev over the last ~5 years.

#Javascript/#WebDev/#WebComponents/#NodeJS have all been the bread and butter for years, would happily continue with that kind of work as well.
